#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-kbookmarkmerger.1.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A program for merging a given set of bookmarks into the user's list of "
"bookmarks."
msgstr "दत्तं पुस्तकचिह्नसमूहं उपयोक्तुः पुस्तकचिह्नसूचौ विलीनीकरणार्थं कार्यक्रमः ।"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
