"बुकमार्क</filename></command>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbookmarkmerger.1.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Merges all bookmark files stored in <filename>/usr/local/extra-bookmarks</"
"filename> into joe's list of bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"<filename>/usr/local/extra-bookmarks</filename> इत्यत्र संगृहीताः सर्वाः "
"पुस्तकचिह्नसञ्चिकाः joe इत्यस्य पुस्तकचिह्नसूचौ विलीनं करोति ।"

